            <div type="translation" resp="part:reda part:emfr">
                
                <p n="1"> 		
                    Prosperity! Fortune!
                </p>
                
                <p n="1">
                    Rod for measuring land.
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>A "+" sign to the left of the inscription marks the beginning of the length of the rod, whereas another "+" sign further to the right of the inscription marks its end. The distance between the two "+" signs, thus the length of the measurement rod, is 4.35 m.</p> 
            </div>
            
